#. Tag: para
#: manual.docbook:3262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">STRIP_VOLUME_RELATIVE</emphasis> : see "
"MASTER_VOLUME_RELATIVE, but applies to the channel strip defined in the "
