#. Tag: para
#: manual.docbook:3267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">STRIP_VOLUME_ABSOLUTE</emphasis> : see "
"MASTER_VOLUME_ABSOLUTE, but applies to the channel strip defined in the "
"Action Parameter **"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: manual.docbook:3272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">EFFECTx_LEVEL_RELATIVE</emphasis> : changes the "
